{"html":"<h2>Tactic(s)</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: mainSourceLemma<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: s<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*St_.*\\(.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*KU\\(~.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*~~&gt;.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*KU\\(KDF\\(.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*KU\\(IBPriv\\(.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*KU\\(idsign\\(.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*KU\\(em\\(.*&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;.*KU\\(pmult\\(.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*!IB_.*&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;.*splitEqs\\(.*&quot;</p><br/>\n","title":"Tactics"}